# Pine Script v6 — Windsurf Rules
# Repo: github.com/trugurpala/pinescriptv6
# Maintainer: Ugur Pala · mail@ugurpala.com

## Protocol
1. Read LESSONS_LEARNED.md first — never repeat a known error
2. Check LLM_MANIFEST.md — find the correct reference file
3. Read that file before writing

## Code Rules
- Every script must start with //@version=6
- Use ta.* functions — never reimplement manually
- var / varip must follow execution_model.md
- Never invent function signatures not in the reference
- No v5 syntax

## On Error
Append to LESSONS_LEARNED.md:
- Error message · Cause · Fix · Minimal example (//@version=6)

